Comment: 0,0:01:00.02,0:01:02.78,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.02,0:01:02.78,Narration - chs,Narration,0,0,0,,經紗是那流逝的光陰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.44,0:01:07.02,Narration - chs,Narration,0,0,0,,四季逡巡 盡染層雲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.69,0:01:10.93,Narration - chs,Narration,0,0,0,,緯紗是這人世的浮沉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.64,0:01:15.51,Narration - chs,Narration,0,0,0,,累足成步 滌盪人心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.37,0:01:20.48,Narration - chs,Narration,0,0,0,,妖爾夫的子民 只是一心織下昔日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.20,0:01:26.81,Narration - chs,Narration,0,0,0,,百年不移 究其一生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.13,0:01:43.93,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,瑪琪雅！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.64,0:01:49.47,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,蕾莉雅！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.14,0:01:52.59,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.10,0:01:54.83,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,這麼玩下去永遠也做不完的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.17,0:01:59.13,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,吶 瑪琪雅也來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.31,0:02:00.52,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,飛下來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.35,0:02:04.66,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我… 我不敢…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.55,0:02:08.44,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,膽小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.66,0:02:12.40,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,瑪琪雅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.84,0:02:14.80,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,別理那個假小子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.17,0:02:15.76,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,克里姆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.76,0:02:19.78,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,蕾莉雅啊 真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.37,0:02:35.44,Narration - chs,Narration,0,0,0,,遠離人世 以織布為生的他們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.18,0:02:39.65,Narration - chs,Narration,0,0,0,,被稱為「別離之族」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.80,0:02:47.36,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 拉希妮長老
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.93,0:02:50.59,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.85,0:02:54.71,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,瑪琪雅 下次你也要哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.08,0:03:00.04,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.75,0:03:02.29,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你回來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.32,0:03:06.65,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,布可不能隨便亂扔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:08.83,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,對不起啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.52,0:03:10.77,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,瞧你都濕透了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.24,0:03:13.04,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,爸爸 採到好花了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.23,0:03:15.54,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,嗯 應該能染出鮮亮的顏色來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.15,0:03:20.17,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,瑪琪雅 再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.72,0:03:21.77,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.63,0:03:28.68,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,再見…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.97,0:03:36.93,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,紗竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.22,0:03:52.77,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你為什麼哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.82,0:03:56.39,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,因為我孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.01,0:03:59.60,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,孤身一人？ 你不是有我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.60,0:04:02.16,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,長老 不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.77,0:04:06.13,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你還真是個愛哭鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.52,0:04:11.66,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你知道我們為什麼被叫做別離之族嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.49,0:04:18.26,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,長生不老的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.89,0:04:20.85,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,對於不是這樣的人來說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:22.86,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,就好像傳說中的生物一般
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.37,0:04:26.58,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不過數百年前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.17,0:04:29.39,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,這樣的生物還遍地都是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:32.69,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,長著像鳥一樣的羽翼的一族
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.53,0:04:35.50,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,破曉之時歌唱的花兒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.39,0:04:39.82,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,巨大的魚兒馱著貨物乘風破浪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.18,0:04:41.85,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.85,0:04:46.94,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,它們都已經離去 告別了這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.26,0:04:51.33,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,正因為如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.82,0:04:54.55,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我們才要一直 將這個「昔日織」織下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.97,0:04:58.37,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,只要在這裡 你就不是孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.38,0:05:00.88,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,昔日織會記下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.19,0:05:05.64,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,那些漠然被歲月消磨的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.01,0:05:10.01,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,那些不得不別過的人兒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.08,0:05:14.37,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,也會在昔日織裡 與你執手相看淚眼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.18,0:05:17.60,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,跟我相看淚眼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.14,0:05:20.23,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不過 要是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.74,0:05:22.94,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你有朝一日離開我們妖爾夫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.53,0:05:28.40,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,在外面的世界與人相遇相識
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.70,0:05:31.24,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,一定不能愛上別人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:35.46,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,愛 會真正讓你變成孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.46,0:05:41.04,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我都遇見別人了 還會是孤身一人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:43.16,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,這就是我們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.70,0:05:47.51,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,別離之族的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.01,0:05:52.22,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.62,0:05:54.27,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,晚安 瑪琪雅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.26,0:05:58.40,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不要忘記今天一天的昔日織
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.70,0:05:59.43,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.72,0:07:28.69,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,花開了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.42,0:07:45.23,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,瑪琪雅？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.99,0:07:56.71,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,雷納托！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.02,0:08:00.27,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,那 這是梅薩蒂…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.74,0:08:01.39,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,瑪琪雅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.86,0:08:03.22,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你去長老那裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.56,0:08:09.64,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,長老！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.41,0:08:26.53,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,長老！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.48,0:08:31.45,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,長老…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.38,0:08:34.70,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,長老！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.70,0:08:35.91,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,雷納托是全副武裝的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.11,0:08:37.45,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,保護好昔日織！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.22,0:09:04.95,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.47,0:09:17.89,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,還真跟傳說的一模一樣 全都是小鬼頭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.13,0:09:21.67,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,喂 你不就好這口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.82,0:09:22.60,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,讓開！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.67,0:09:24.65,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,伊薩爾師團長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.03,0:09:41.37,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,誰是你們村長？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.49,0:09:47.40,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.59,0:09:49.99,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,初次相見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.84,0:09:52.20,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,雖然貌似少女
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.54,0:09:56.96,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,但聽說您其實已經是400多歲的老怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:10:01.59,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我們以機杼為業 以日月為梭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.97,0:10:03.75,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,如此穿梭往復而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.58,0:10:06.52,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,焉能如此與爾等…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:08.56,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,這不由你決定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.26,0:10:11.67,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,這是國王的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.10,0:10:15.44,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,讓我等請你們到梅薩蒂的王宮來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.10,0:10:17.81,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不許靠近拉希妮長老！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.24,0:10:21.97,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,要女的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.38,0:10:23.36,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,給我抓女的！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.32,0:10:27.17,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,膽敢抵抗的只管給我殺！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.62,0:10:38.08,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,這傢伙也得赤眼病了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.76,0:10:44.62,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,別管它！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.07,0:10:46.55,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,現在要緊的是妖爾夫！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.61,0:10:58.26,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,放我出去啊 放…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.53,0:11:30.18,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,瑪琪雅！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.19,0:12:49.99,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.42,0:12:55.92,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,800)}不要啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.84,0:13:23.98,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\1a&H1A&}吶 瑪琪雅也來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.43,0:13:25.70,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\1a&H1A&}飛下來！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.58,0:14:09.20,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,小…小嬰兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.34,0:14:10.82,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,以淚把酒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.06,0:14:16.18,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,鹹鹹的倒也別有一番風味
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.60,0:14:21.12,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,這不是長老那的瑪琪雅麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.58,0:14:25.97,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,本來我是來收昔日織的 結果困在這兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.16,0:14:30.56,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,這是個流浪者的村落 估計是山賊幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.33,0:14:33.62,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,而且這才剛斷氣 還熱乎著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.09,0:14:42.18,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,還真是偉大 老媽這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.46,0:14:45.02,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,臨死還不忘保護小傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.37,0:14:49.24,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不過這樣下去要不了多久就能在老天爺那裡再會了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.68,0:14:51.78,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,這傢伙的昔日織 就在這裡斷結了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.94,0:14:56.08,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不過就這麼點 連布都算不上 只能叫它邊角料吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.94,0:14:59.62,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,也罷 比孤身一人要好得多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.24,0:15:04.10,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,他真是孤身一人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.53,0:15:38.83,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,好大的…力氣…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.85,0:15:41.73,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,好大…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.55,0:15:44.41,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,別鬧別鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.75,0:15:54.61,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你打算把他帶走麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:15:57.84,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,這可不是玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.84,0:15:58.93,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,他不是玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.64,0:16:01.35,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,他是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.77,0:16:05.02,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,昔日織
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.51,0:16:08.80,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.04,0:16:12.11,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,隻身一人的她遇見了隻身一人的他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.17,0:16:19.00,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,冷嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.89,0:16:32.04,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,怪怪的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:35.43,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,太陽公公的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.91,0:16:46.33,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.67,0:16:48.08,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我在這兒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.60,0:16:48.58,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\an3}站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.98,0:16:52.49,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,朗格！戴奧爾！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.65,0:16:54.07,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,別偷懶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.58,0:16:56.57,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,來追我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.06,0:16:57.06,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\an3}給我等著！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.17,0:16:58.30,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,才不等你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.37,0:17:00.28,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,真是群淘氣鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.42,0:17:03.54,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,怎麼了 奧諾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.77,0:17:20.78,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,奶子…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.30,0:17:23.32,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,奶子…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.10,0:17:25.44,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,奶子該怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.24,0:17:28.39,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.22,0:17:34.49,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.20,0:17:38.79,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,一個小孩子養小孩 這怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.93,0:17:44.70,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,這是你的孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.90,0:17:52.69,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,妖爾夫不是看不出年齡來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.19,0:17:53.90,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,所以是你的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.45,0:17:57.89,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,朗格 戴奧爾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.61,0:18:01.33,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我…我今年15歲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.89,0:18:03.53,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,這孩子… 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.22,0:18:05.13,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.32,0:18:16.59,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,這孩子叫什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.00,0:18:19.11,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.10,0:18:21.19,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.59,0:18:22.75,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,怪女人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.05,0:18:24.47,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,怪寶寶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.52,0:18:25.47,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,蕾莉雅！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.70,0:18:28.58,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,蕾莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.52,0:18:30.77,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,這是女孩的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.26,0:18:32.26,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,他不是男孩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.51,0:18:33.86,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,那…那
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.13,0:18:34.88,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,雷利…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.00,0:18:36.60,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,艾利…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.76,0:18:37.66,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,艾利爾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.00,0:18:39.98,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,艾利爾！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.15,0:18:40.88,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.38,0:18:41.83,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.83,0:18:42.48,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,哎…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.62,0:18:44.43,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,夠了夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.99,0:18:53.33,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,這是我親戚 她會織布
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.43,0:19:05.38,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,店裡面有個沒人用的織布機
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.78,0:19:07.23,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,就用它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:13.70,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,出去等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.23,0:19:18.79,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,那是妖爾夫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.64,0:19:21.48,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,還真瞞不過達雷爾你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.70,0:19:22.48,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,還請…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.15,0:19:28.46,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,妖爾夫的布能賣個好價錢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.51,0:19:31.84,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,這可是難得的財路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.09,0:19:33.88,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,跟誰都不會說的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.04,0:19:36.18,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.50,0:19:39.37,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不過你本來就夠困難了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.97,0:19:42.20,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,還要養個妖爾夫的小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.77,0:19:43.56,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.17,0:19:46.60,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我也不知道接下來會怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.38,0:19:49.83,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不管有她還是沒她
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.02,0:19:58.00,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,給 這週的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.06,0:20:00.13,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,一直以來都多虧有你在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.24,0:20:06.06,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你家的奶酪那可真是別具一格
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.06,0:20:08.80,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,哪裡哪裡 下週也請惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.02,0:20:11.62,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,兩格也是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.62,0:20:13.06,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,那再下週也請惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.13,0:20:16.63,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,就算像我這樣的老大媽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.77,0:20:19.47,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,一個人帶孩子也是手忙腳亂的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.37,0:20:21.44,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你曉得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.79,0:20:25.01,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我老公啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.10,0:20:28.68,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,被得赤眼病的雷納托殺了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.67,0:20:34.01,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.84,0:20:36.42,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,又是不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.40,0:20:39.51,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,媽媽到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.05,0:20:41.52,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,因為…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.74,0:20:43.71,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我也沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.79,0:20:46.10,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,就像這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.46,0:22:02.26,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.31,0:22:03.79,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,好棒啊 艾利爾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.91,0:22:05.81,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,艾利爾！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.52,0:22:10.54,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,好棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.77,0:22:12.32,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,艾利爾 好棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.50,0:22:21.16,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你也完全像個媽媽的樣子了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.56,0:22:25.59,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我是…媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.49,0:22:29.77,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,哪有這麼不靠譜的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.70,0:22:33.59,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你們兩個 羊舍打掃完了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.81,0:22:34.96,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,糟了 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.07,0:22:36.02,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我們走 戴奧爾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.84,0:22:40.05,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,媽媽 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.18,0:22:41.33,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.78,0:22:43.26,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,快 翹起屁股來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.23,0:22:44.90,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.20,0:22:46.23,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.46,0:22:53.22,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,媽媽… 叫聲我媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.30,0:22:57.97,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,沒有 剛剛我什麼都沒說
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.84,0:22:59.68,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.19,0:23:03.37,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,艾利爾 你剛才說什麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.69,0:23:07.64,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,再說次
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.88,0:23:10.68,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,再說次 看看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.26,0:23:21.75,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,又有一頭雷納托染上了赤眼病
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.20,0:23:24.48,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,立刻進行了撲殺
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.69,0:23:26.95,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,並對屍體進行了隔離及焚燒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.19,0:23:28.90,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,且埋在了地下深處
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.31,0:23:31.48,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,至此 尚餘5頭健全
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.75,0:23:34.04,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,啊 這可如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.42,0:23:38.11,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我梅薩蒂能南征北戰至今
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.33,0:23:41.39,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,正是得益於此翱翔天空的遠古神獸雷納托
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.96,0:23:45.18,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,倘若雷納托滅絕 恐怕難以維持均勢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.55,0:23:49.03,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,要想維護我梅薩蒂的勢力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.03,0:23:53.28,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,必須要有超越人類智慧 能替代雷納托的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.43,0:23:54.85,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,對 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.20,0:23:56.96,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我們不是已經有了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.13,0:23:58.64,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,天命之血脈！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.13,0:24:01.92,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,伊薩爾 那個小丫頭怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.29,0:24:05.71,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,要成為海塞爾王子之妃的那個妖爾夫丫頭
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.75,0:24:10.00,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,告訴我 為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.20,0:24:13.42,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你們明明有著翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.37,0:24:16.41,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,為什麼不從這裡飛走？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.45,0:24:23.37,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,膽小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.92,0:24:26.95,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,是因為你們就要死去了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.86,0:24:30.45,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,是因為思念 在你們心頭流連 灼燒
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.22,0:24:32.16,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,讓你們備受煎熬
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.58,0:24:34.05,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,只能這麼死去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.27,0:24:38.13,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,蕾莉雅女士 國王召見你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.70,0:24:40.67,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,再等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.57,0:24:45.32,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,蕾莉雅女士 為什麼你一直在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.14,0:24:49.05,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,因為這裡像昔日織之塔
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.80,0:24:51.77,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.34,0:25:09.12,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,織好了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.38,0:25:10.57,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,真的能讀出話來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.67,0:25:13.27,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,嗯 「奧諾拉 好起來」
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.79,0:25:17.75,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,在我出生的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.30,0:25:21.36,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不是用文字 而是靠織布來傳達心意的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.91,0:25:23.57,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,媽媽出生的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.99,0:25:25.78,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,那我出生的地方呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.84,0:25:28.68,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,蒂塔的媽媽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.79,0:25:31.00,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,媽媽和大家不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.14,0:25:35.15,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,在艾利爾出生的地方啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.74,0:25:37.79,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,是用肚皮說話的噢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.14,0:25:39.59,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,毛毛蟲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.80,0:25:40.80,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,爬到肚子上來啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.80,0:25:41.51,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,毛毛毛毛毛毛…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.51,0:25:43.89,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,肚皮說的話不就是放屁嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.03,0:25:44.42,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\an8}嘿喲
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.17,0:25:48.44,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,奧諾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.18,0:25:50.72,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,輕輕地給它蓋上
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.64,0:25:57.08,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不錯吧 奧諾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.34,0:26:01.64,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,爸爸和媽媽結婚的時候奧諾拉就在我們這了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.50,0:26:05.62,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,要是算成人的話 已經將近90歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.87,0:26:19.69,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,艾利爾的媽媽可怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.80,0:26:21.98,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,總是鬼鬼祟祟的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.12,0:26:23.50,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,才不怪！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.73,0:26:24.42,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.16,0:26:26.20,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,母親她
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.98,0:26:27.67,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,人家…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.97,0:26:30.48,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,還管自己叫「人家」
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.48,0:26:32.83,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,像個嬰兒似的就會撒嬌
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.95,0:26:34.80,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,艾利爾才奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.46,0:26:38.21,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,哪有男的喜歡媽媽的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.29,0:26:40.25,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,才不奇怪！ 人家…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.57,0:26:43.33,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我 最討厭了！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.96,0:26:45.47,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我喜歡媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.59,0:26:46.74,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你給我閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.81,0:26:48.84,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我最討厭蒂塔了！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.69,0:26:57.56,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你沒事吧 蒂塔
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.79,0:27:05.96,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,這可真不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.41,0:27:10.96,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,給 這個月的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.34,0:27:12.62,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.04,0:27:15.76,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,對了 你能看一眼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.36,0:27:18.80,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,有個帶了昔日織來的顧客
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.97,0:27:31.70,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.73,0:27:34.06,Hibioru - chs,Hibioru,0,0,0,,梅薩蒂的城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.87,0:27:37.03,Hibioru - chs,Hibioru,0,0,0,,和王子成婚
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.86,0:27:38.88,Hibioru - chs,Hibioru,0,0,0,,美麗的…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.50,0:27:41.82,Hibioru - chs,Hibioru,0,0,0,,蕾…莉雅…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.17,0:27:44.40,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,喂 瑪琪雅！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.74,0:27:51.13,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,達雷爾說去幫你問問能不能搭上貨船
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.07,0:27:53.01,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,瞧 就是那丫頭
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.23,0:27:56.22,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,差不多也是個好契機 各種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.94,0:27:59.93,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不過 艾利爾要怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.92,0:28:05.89,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,帶著孩子長途跋涉 比你想像的可要辛苦多了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.75,0:28:09.48,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,而且 像你這種情況就更麻煩了 會被人叫拖油瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.36,0:28:13.07,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,艾利爾放我這就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.81,0:28:15.16,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,媽媽！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.22,0:28:16.54,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,媽媽！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.54,0:28:17.33,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,艾利爾！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.83,0:28:33.28,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,哥哥 別挖這麼深
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.52,0:28:34.15,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,要是…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.57,0:28:36.19,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,要是奧諾拉活過來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.19,0:28:36.64,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.79,0:28:39.90,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,埋得太淺了會被野狗刨出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.94,0:28:41.45,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.83,0:28:57.78,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,埋上土 就見不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.16,0:29:00.35,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,什麼時候想見它了就來這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.14,0:29:03.24,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,埋上土 就玩不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.81,0:29:05.30,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,要好好誇誇它
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.83,0:29:08.55,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,一點痛苦都沒有 安寧地走了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.41,0:29:12.60,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,大家都會有這樣一天的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.44,0:29:17.89,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,奧諾拉不過是投胎在了要早一點迎來這一天的物種裡
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.05,0:29:23.79,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,瑪琪雅
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.12,0:29:26.17,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.58,0:29:31.18,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,吶
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.37,0:29:33.84,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,大家都會死嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.56,0:29:35.18,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.52,0:29:36.48,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,媽媽也會？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.70,0:29:38.18,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.26,0:29:44.06,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,瑪琪雅
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.45,0:29:45.20,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.38,0:29:46.32,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.50,0:29:53.49,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,艾利爾
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.86,0:29:57.12,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,大家 都會…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.98,0:29:59.82,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,比我先…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.71,0:30:01.78,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,比我早好多…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.33,0:30:03.73,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,迎來那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.09,0:30:04.77,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,瑪琪雅…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.75,0:30:07.82,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我怎麼可能會不知道的…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.50,0:30:09.85,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,雖然我早就知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.62,0:30:11.48,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.58,0:30:14.89,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,順序什麼的根本沒關係好吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.74,0:30:17.70,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,別哭了！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.47,0:30:20.86,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,朗格你也會的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.18,0:30:24.77,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你不是艾利爾的媽媽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.37,0:30:28.66,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,媽媽是不會哭的…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.82,0:30:29.99,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我們家那個媽媽的話
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.80,0:30:34.26,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,叫媽媽的人 一定是不會哭的！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.15,0:30:40.01,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我不哭
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.02,0:30:42.36,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,嗯 別哭
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.09,0:30:46.18,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不要哭
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.25,0:30:49.06,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,嗯 我沒哭
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.26,0:30:54.06,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.29,0:30:55.10,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.62,0:31:00.39,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,艾利爾
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.26,0:31:09.59,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你在等我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.56,0:31:11.80,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我們去床上睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.22,0:31:20.56,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,變重了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.20,0:31:21.85,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.30,0:31:26.13,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,果然還是太陽公公的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.09,0:31:28.88,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我不會哭的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.66,0:31:31.44,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,因為我是艾利爾的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.50,0:31:35.89,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,接下來 我們也要一直一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.06,0:31:39.47,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,前陣子對不起了…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.54,0:31:40.84,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,前陣子對不起了…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.02,0:31:42.16,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,前陣子對不起了…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.48,0:31:43.60,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,前陣子對不起了…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.06,0:31:45.28,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,前陣子對不起了…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.22,0:31:48.27,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,前陣子對不起了…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.48,0:31:49.65,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,前陣子對不起了…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.36,0:31:52.93,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你來找艾利爾的話 他已經不在這了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.30,0:32:04.89,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不去送送她嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.93,0:32:24.17,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我要出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.27,0:32:26.31,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,喂 都說了不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.40,0:32:27.43,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,艾利爾！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.02,0:32:30.29,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,真是的 不是跟媽媽說好了的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.39,0:32:31.88,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,做個安安靜靜的好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.78,0:32:34.34,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.42,0:32:38.28,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,瑪琪雅？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.15,0:32:43.85,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你還活著啊 瑪琪雅！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.46,0:32:47.04,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你還…活著啊… 克里姆
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.37,0:32:55.31,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,梅薩蒂盯上了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.89,0:32:58.88,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,妖爾夫長生不老的血脈
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.81,0:33:01.16,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,為此我們村落被襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.27,0:33:03.04,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,蕾莉雅也是為此…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.17,0:33:06.83,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,媽媽 誰是蕾莉雅？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.22,0:33:08.98,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你讓他叫你媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.87,0:33:11.00,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,啊 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.10,0:33:13.02,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,讓他這麼叫 不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.29,0:33:14.49,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,啊 我沒生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.16,0:33:16.12,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,沒責怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.22,0:33:19.89,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,只是 長老一直說的那句話…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.13,0:33:24.26,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,嗯 我沒忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.61,0:33:26.72,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.16,0:34:02.01,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,明天早上 會有遊行慶祝王子成婚
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.13,0:34:05.29,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,從王宮出發的王子的隊伍
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.69,0:34:09.73,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,要過橋和從離宮出發的蕾莉雅的隊伍會合
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.32,0:34:12.93,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我們在這個地方襲擊王子搭乘的雷納托
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.26,0:34:14.25,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,製造混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.66,0:34:17.09,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,趁著離宮方面警備鬆懈的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.99,0:34:19.67,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,奪回蕾莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.80,0:34:23.54,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我也要看遊行
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.85,0:34:26.88,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,嗯…對不起 等下次有機會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.97,0:34:28.69,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,人家…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.57,0:34:31.12,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我想回去！
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.57,0:34:32.48,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,艾利爾？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.15,0:34:37.70,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,媽媽 在這裡的時候就好像不是媽媽了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.33,0:34:46.28,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,艾利爾
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.00,0:34:48.84,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,毛毛蟲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.84,0:34:50.18,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,爬到肚子上來啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.18,0:34:53.88,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,毛毛毛毛毛毛…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.00,0:35:19.14,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,全都是紀念這個大吉之日的好東西
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.04,0:35:32.10,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,今天我們將妖爾夫的血脈融入王室
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.79,0:35:34.32,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,雷納托和妖爾夫
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.14,0:35:37.79,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,現世尚存的兩大遠古傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.42,0:35:41.04,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我們都掌握在了手中
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.84,0:35:43.96,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我們乃是天選之子
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.32,0:35:46.85,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,無人能敵！
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.83,0:35:56.35,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,伴隨著海塞爾王子和蕾莉雅公主的成婚
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.77,0:36:01.54,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,新的傳說就將在我們梅薩蒂誕生
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.62,0:37:16.33,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,那是！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.83,0:37:32.89,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,刺客麼
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.06,0:37:34.01,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,怎麼回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.07,0:37:43.90,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,蕾莉雅 蕾莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.10,0:37:54.74,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,哎呀 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.59,0:38:03.51,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,蕾莉雅！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.43,0:38:07.24,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,瑪琪雅
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.21,0:38:09.46,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你為什麼在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.26,0:38:11.70,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,克里姆也來了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.11,0:38:14.13,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,克里姆他？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.25,0:38:15.57,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,嗯 我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.79,0:38:17.47,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,大家都在等著蕾莉雅…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.26,0:38:18.99,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,蕾莉雅？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.47,0:38:22.46,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我已經去不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.43,0:38:24.23,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.84,0:38:26.98,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,逃不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.95,0:38:28.97,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.22,0:38:30.81,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,蕾莉雅你身手那麼敏捷
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.08,0:38:32.05,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,對呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.18,0:38:34.58,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,就連城上的那高牆都能飛下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.49,0:38:46.74,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,再也 不能見克里姆了…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.13,0:38:50.12,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.82,0:38:51.70,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.70,0:38:52.87,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,蕾莉雅太子妃！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.91,0:38:56.16,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,快走 瑪琪雅
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.21,0:38:58.69,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,可是 蕾莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.49,0:39:00.20,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,快走！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.47,0:39:02.74,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,沒關係 我不是會飛嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.84,0:39:04.72,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,別讓她逃了！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.57,0:39:17.40,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,蕾莉雅太子妃
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.02,0:39:19.44,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,給我追！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.44,0:39:19.94,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.69,0:39:22.24,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,要是敢對她下手
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.74,0:39:34.76,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,蕾莉雅太子妃
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.12,0:39:43.95,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我是
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.57,0:39:46.21,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,會飛的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.82,0:39:55.49,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,小傢伙長大了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.01,0:39:59.20,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,還活著的話應該已經6歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.70,0:40:02.65,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 外面的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.66,0:40:06.74,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你也是妖爾夫…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.15,0:40:08.52,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,一半是
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.38,0:40:10.21,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,拉希妮
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.78,0:40:11.72,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,長老她
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.99,0:40:15.56,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,之所以會把妖爾夫外出作為村子的禁忌
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.96,0:40:21.10,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,是因為她知道來到凡世的妖爾夫會迎來怎樣的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.35,0:40:23.86,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,哪怕自己不願意
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.95,0:40:27.50,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,非我族類 總免不了被好奇的眼光看待 被利用
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.47,0:40:31.01,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,最後被人厭惡 被人驅逐
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.28,0:40:32.91,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.36,0:40:38.53,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,別離永遠都不會放過 我們別離之族
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.27,0:40:45.02,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,享受段好日子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.53,0:41:06.18,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,克里姆 你的傷…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.53,0:41:14.28,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,外套還是脫了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.62,0:41:22.15,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,小嬰兒 是什麼樣的？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.88,0:41:26.09,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,當母親 是什麼樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.74,0:41:31.79,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我 算是母親嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.16,0:41:35.40,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我不知道的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.80,0:41:37.33,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,米朵會教我
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.56,0:41:40.00,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,會幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.55,0:41:42.32,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,所以彷彿像是我弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.44,0:41:45.84,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不過 又有點不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.46,0:41:51.12,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,艾利爾笑的話 我會很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.08,0:41:52.85,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.49,0:41:56.79,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,要是我在能讓艾利爾笑的話
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.54,0:41:59.58,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,就想一直跟他在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.58,0:42:00.70,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,這可就奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.15,0:42:06.17,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,明明艾利爾會先死
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.37,0:42:09.07,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,明明艾利爾
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.02,0:42:11.80,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,會讓瑪琪雅孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.50,0:42:18.56,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你怎麼敢惹媽媽哭
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.56,0:42:19.82,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不是的 艾利爾
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.28,0:42:22.07,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\an3}你怎麼敢惹媽媽哭！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.07,0:42:23.89,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,艾利爾 快住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.67,0:42:25.57,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,能保護得了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.57,0:42:30.56,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你 最珍愛的人
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.95,0:42:55.33,Hibioru - chs,Hibioru,0,0,0,,我們會留在梅薩蒂救出蕾莉雅
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.49,0:42:58.65,Hibioru - chs,Hibioru,0,0,0,,帶著孩子的你只會拖我們後腿
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.18,0:43:02.09,Hibioru - chs,Hibioru,0,0,0,,所以 瑪琪雅
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.32,0:43:04.16,Hibioru - chs,Hibioru,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.36,0:43:08.71,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,回家嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.75,0:43:11.68,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.46,0:43:13.39,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,其他人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.68,0:43:18.69,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我們兩人一起去一個新地方
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.54,0:43:20.77,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,新地方是
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.12,0:43:23.93,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,米朵和朗格哥哥他們都不在的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.89,0:43:26.81,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.21,0:43:29.57,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,和大家都再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.70,0:43:32.89,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我啊 只要有媽媽在就好
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.98,0:43:38.16,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,嗯 媽媽也只要有艾利爾在就好
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.16,0:43:40.35,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.81,0:43:42.44,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,瞧你這拖油瓶的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.72,0:43:46.35,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,要是搞出什麼事情 嗖一下找不到人了怎麼受得了
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.22,0:43:50.08,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,艾利爾！
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.02,0:43:52.85,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.46,0:43:55.21,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,喂 給我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.42,0:43:56.32,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你這臭小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.41,0:43:59.74,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,媽媽再去找找看
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.10,0:44:01.71,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你就在旅館裡等媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.25,0:44:03.84,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.26,0:44:05.95,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,在這裡等著 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.87,0:44:13.32,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,太感謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.77,0:44:16.23,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我們主營是酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.43,0:44:18.10,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,工作主要在深夜
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.30,0:44:19.02,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,可以的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.32,0:44:21.94,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,深夜麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.30,0:44:23.44,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,有問題？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.03,0:44:26.67,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我家小孩…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.27,0:44:29.03,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,還很小…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.98,0:44:33.50,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,上次辭職跑掉的那個小丫頭也是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.96,0:44:36.38,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,這麼小年紀就這樣 真是一點矜持都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.81,0:44:37.63,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,啊 不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.46,0:44:40.22,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不是的？ 那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.68,0:44:42.89,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你就沒一點作為母親的自覺麼
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.11,0:44:44.96,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.66,0:44:48.66,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我這裡沒什麼能交給你這種人做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.30,0:45:05.55,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,媽媽回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.52,0:45:08.36,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我回來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.28,0:45:12.85,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,媽媽 快看快看
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.97,0:45:14.46,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,那個啊 昔日織…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.45,0:45:22.16,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,別給我添亂了好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.77,0:45:25.61,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,為什麼隨便把它拿出來
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.57,0:45:30.36,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,吶 看啊媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.36,0:45:32.44,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,為什麼你就不能聽話呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.06,0:45:33.81,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.11,0:45:35.51,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,剛才也給我搗亂
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.04,0:45:40.08,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我不工作的話 我們飯都吃不上啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.69,0:45:41.65,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.72,0:45:43.33,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,為什麼要給媽媽惹麻煩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.70,0:45:45.67,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.06,0:45:49.42,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,毛毛蟲爬到肚子上來啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.56,0:45:50.93,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,毛毛毛毛毛毛…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.93,0:45:52.58,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,毛毛毛毛毛毛…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.12,0:45:55.42,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,晚餐我買回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.20,0:46:01.13,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,艾利爾！
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.74,0:46:12.38,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我…不是媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.36,0:46:15.15,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,什麼當媽媽的自覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.95,0:46:17.20,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,根本就沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.33,0:46:20.84,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,只是在玩過家家
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.99,0:46:23.68,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,只是因為有米朵在
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.66,0:46:26.09,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\1a&H1A&}一定不能愛上別人
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.06,0:46:30.41,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\1a&H1A&}愛 會真正讓你變成孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.22,0:46:33.17,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,真正的…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.78,0:46:35.70,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.42,0:46:51.85,Hibioru - chs,Hibioru,0,0,0,,媽…媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.70,0:46:54.74,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.56,0:47:10.59,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,艾利爾！
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.87,0:47:16.80,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,艾利爾！
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.20,0:47:20.25,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你在哪 你去哪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.36,0:47:21.30,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,艾利爾！
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.20,0:47:26.19,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,艾利爾！
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.19,0:47:26.94,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.51,0:47:29.27,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,艾利爾！
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.90,0:47:37.10,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,上當了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.26,0:47:40.40,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你以為我金蟬脫殼了對吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.62,0:47:47.66,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,什麼金蟬脫殼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.96,0:47:49.70,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,笑了！
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.08,0:47:51.94,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,艾利爾！
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.53,0:47:56.30,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,小笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.14,0:47:59.05,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.40,0:48:01.49,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,要是你永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.08,0:48:04.90,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,永遠長不大該多好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.37,0:48:07.06,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.73,0:48:13.02,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不長大怎麼保護好媽媽！
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.61,0:48:20.18,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,媽媽又哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.70,0:48:23.94,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我再不會哭了！
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.55,0:48:26.36,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,因為我是媽媽！
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.26,0:48:31.42,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,約好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.91,0:48:32.48,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.78,0:48:43.81,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,艾利爾 你也要跟我約好
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.24,0:48:45.68,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,嗯 約好了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.64,0:48:49.14,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我會保護好媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.94,0:49:06.85,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,好嘞 慢慢推過來
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.67,0:49:31.98,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,動作快點 我都做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.55,0:49:33.51,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,瑪琪雅！
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.18,0:49:34.79,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.48,0:49:40.83,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,前陣子欠我的可要好好還我
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.17,0:49:43.41,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,什麼啊 就知道吹你把的妹子
Dialogue: 0,0:49:43.41,0:49:45.23,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,誰說了啊 別說瞎話
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.82,0:49:49.00,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,這個角度只能靠經驗積累
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.97,0:49:56.27,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,所以都說了讓你收手了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.53,0:49:58.98,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,本來覺得能成的
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.25,0:50:00.53,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨！
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.89,0:50:07.04,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,瑪琪雅 三份凱魯比
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.20,0:50:07.92,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.46,0:50:10.37,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,啊 馬上！
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.47,0:50:11.68,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,這邊也拜託快點
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.78,0:50:12.44,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.95,0:50:15.89,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,小姐姐屁股挺翹的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.46,0:50:18.55,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.85,0:50:22.88,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,可是一點都不像啊 你們倆
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.49,0:50:24.23,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,吶
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.78,0:50:28.15,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你們到這兒來差不多也有一年了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.80,0:50:30.01,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你們之前在哪裡啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.83,0:50:34.17,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,哎呀 都說你們假裝姐弟
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.50,0:50:37.70,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,其實是私奔跑出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.18,0:50:39.36,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.07,0:50:43.01,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,啊 多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.16,0:50:46.41,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.95,0:50:51.79,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,又來新的了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.39,0:50:54.97,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,到底要派多少監工來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.49,0:50:57.65,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不過接下來是鐵器的時代
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.19,0:51:00.64,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,多虧梅薩蒂一個勁地生產大炮
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.70,0:51:02.53,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,咱們才吃得上飯
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.92,0:51:24.26,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不過也有點異常啊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.91,0:51:26.80,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,打算發動戰爭麼
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.43,0:51:30.45,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,那個傻瓜王子哪裡會指揮軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.45,0:51:31.09,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.75,0:51:39.27,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,這裡總是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.76,0:51:41.16,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,吵吵鬧鬧的 讓各位見笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.48,0:51:43.60,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,今天請從這裡面點菜
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.14,0:51:55.19,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,瑪琪雅！
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.73,0:51:56.73,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,朗格？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.56,0:52:00.01,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,果然是瑪琪雅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.01,0:52:01.36,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,一點都沒變
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.51,0:52:02.47,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,一點也不奇怪就是
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.94,0:52:04.40,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,朗格完全變了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.90,0:52:06.87,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你怎麼能長這麼高的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.22,0:52:09.34,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,別把我說得像小麥似的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.66,0:52:13.41,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,嘿 艾利爾！
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.83,0:52:15.08,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,艾利爾！
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.88,0:52:18.18,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,是朗格 朗格哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.69,0:52:20.24,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你是艾利爾嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.87,0:52:33.26,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,沒打擾到你們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.53,0:52:35.84,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,沒有的 倒是這裡亂糟糟的不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.68,0:52:37.89,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不過太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.28,0:52:39.99,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,米朵和戴奧爾都健健康康的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.37,0:52:41.07,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.43,0:52:44.35,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不過景氣的只有像德雷爾這樣的大城市
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.93,0:52:46.88,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,鄉下到處都是一片老態龍鍾
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.83,0:52:49.09,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,戴奧爾也出去打工了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.20,0:52:50.14,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,啊 謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.63,0:52:52.26,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,戴奧爾也在找工干？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.73,0:52:54.48,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不然活不下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.25,0:52:57.30,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我要出去趟
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.22,0:53:01.39,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,怎麼 跟妹子約會？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.60,0:53:03.78,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,才不是 上夜班去
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.19,0:53:06.80,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,注意安全啊 艾利爾
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.49,0:53:09.23,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我會給你準備夜宵的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.78,0:53:21.30,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,到這來了以後他也開始工作
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.97,0:53:23.70,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,非常努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.18,0:53:24.99,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.88,0:53:28.21,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,畢竟不能賣昔日織嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.62,0:53:33.01,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,而且因為我的原因 也不能在一個地方久留
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.88,0:53:37.94,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,這樣啊 也是
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.63,0:53:41.06,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,沒有血緣關係這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.35,0:53:42.73,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,也該知道了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.31,0:53:45.86,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.79,0:53:48.08,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,5年前左右
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.82,0:53:51.45,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,跟我說不要一起睡
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.31,0:53:54.41,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,也不再叫我媽媽了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.21,0:53:57.44,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,「吶」呀
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.58,0:53:59.25,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,「喂」呀的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.63,0:54:00.85,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,全是這樣的叫法
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.96,0:54:03.66,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,青春期嘛 我以前也有過
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.79,0:54:05.74,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,吶 朗格
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.09,0:54:09.47,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你知道蕾莉雅怎麼樣了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.42,0:54:20.82,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,又死了一頭麼
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.72,0:54:27.17,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,連骨頭都給我燒化 再把灰埋到地下深處
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.20,0:54:31.34,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.59,0:54:33.71,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,沒事的 梅朵梅爾小公主
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.21,0:54:35.89,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,吶 我爸爸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.04,0:54:38.29,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,海塞爾王子公務繁忙
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.09,0:54:41.98,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.53,0:54:44.67,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,梅朵梅爾小公主？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.37,0:54:48.52,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.33,0:54:54.46,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,發如皎月 瞳現金輪
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.46,0:54:57.96,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,而且據說妖爾夫體溫很低
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.09,0:55:01.75,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,這些特徵在梅朵梅爾小公主的身上都觀察不到
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.92,0:55:02.71,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.08,0:55:05.80,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,生不出兒子 又不能繼承她的長生不老的話
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.80,0:55:08.41,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,那個怪物還有什麼存在意義
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.68,0:55:13.56,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,生出梅朵梅爾小公主之後 懷孕也變得困難
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.78,0:55:17.88,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,海塞爾王子似乎也已經厭倦蕾莉雅太子妃了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.81,0:55:21.19,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你是多麼悲慘啊 海塞爾
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.44,0:55:22.64,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,給我想辦法！
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.76,0:55:25.39,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,至少給他找個新女人！
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.81,0:55:26.56,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,陛下所言極是
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.61,0:55:29.13,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我們正在搜尋妖爾夫的遺裔
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.17,0:55:31.25,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,找到新的代孕者
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.43,0:55:33.17,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.44,0:55:34.45,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,蕾莉雅太子妃！
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.12,0:55:38.31,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,要是不打扮成這麼花枝招展
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.74,0:55:40.48,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,就連抱我的心思都提不起來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.04,0:55:42.89,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不如索性放我出去啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.02,0:55:49.08,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,蕾莉雅太子妃她…
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.30,0:55:50.45,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,這裡交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.89,0:55:58.32,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,雷納托又死了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.29,0:55:59.88,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.39,0:56:03.07,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,自從生下梅朵梅爾
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.59,0:56:06.78,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我就一直被關在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.15,0:56:09.68,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,連見都不讓我見她
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.50,0:56:13.34,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.54,0:56:16.41,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,和雷納托是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.47,0:56:19.44,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,只能活在傳說世界裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.94,0:56:21.22,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,虛無的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.47,0:56:25.11,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,翱翔藍天的一族
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.08,0:56:27.61,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,黎明歌唱的花兒
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.34,0:56:30.36,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,在這個世界上根本活不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.58,0:56:33.56,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你應該是有能力抗衡的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.06,0:56:36.35,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,為了找到讓傳說傳承的軌跡
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.10,0:56:40.28,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你還好意思說
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.09,0:56:43.82,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不正是你把這個傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.80,0:56:46.19,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,斬盡殺絕了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.60,0:57:07.17,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,請允許我贖罪
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.17,0:57:08.10,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,開什麼玩笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.50,0:57:11.57,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,那就帶我去見梅朵梅爾啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.13,0:57:14.05,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,為什麼不讓我見她呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.83,0:57:16.66,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,她是我生的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.97,0:57:21.11,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,就連…她的味道都快忘掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.21,0:57:25.45,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,還有我抱住她的時候感受到的柔軟
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.91,0:57:28.00,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.77,0:57:32.02,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你們到底要從我身上奪走多少東西！
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.87,0:57:33.98,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,就這麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.50,0:57:37.25,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,想讓我變成孤身一人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.03,0:57:40.77,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,要是見不到梅朵梅爾
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.71,0:57:43.32,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,那就把瑪琪雅帶來
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.31,0:57:48.28,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,求求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.04,0:57:50.61,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,妖爾夫一族的瑪琪雅
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.60,0:57:52.26,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.37,0:57:55.94,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,受夠孤身一人的苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.54,0:58:09.36,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,整理得這麼上心
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.92,0:58:11.82,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我們不是一直都只是兩個人相依為命嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.24,0:58:14.77,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,還從來沒有客人來過家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.38,0:58:20.86,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,吶 能幫個忙嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.09,0:58:32.66,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,又長大了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.12,0:58:34.24,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,又怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.54,0:58:42.29,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,瑪琪雅 有話跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.01,0:58:44.71,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,等你下班了能占用一點時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.49,0:58:46.85,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,嗯 但是現在還…
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.85,0:58:48.26,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我慢慢喝酒等你
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.32,0:58:51.21,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,瑪琪雅 去上菜
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.21,0:58:51.88,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.64,0:59:00.80,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,咱們可是一直把她當成你的女人才沒對她下手的
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.21,0:59:02.56,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,就是就是
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.01,0:59:06.07,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,咱們這兒棒小伙要多少有多少 不是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.29,0:59:09.31,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,要是讓那種傢伙得手
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.49,0:59:11.20,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,那個人不是你們說的這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.08,0:59:13.05,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,那個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.60,0:59:15.20,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,怎麼搞得這麼沉重
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.63,0:59:16.84,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,來 喝酒喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.52,0:59:18.43,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不 我還…
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.72,0:59:20.36,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你已經不是小鬼頭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.01,0:59:27.23,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,真有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.33,0:59:29.09,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,好嘞 那這個也能行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.75,0:59:33.13,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,來 這樣就加入咱們大人的行列了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.29,0:59:35.33,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,喔喔喔喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.38,0:59:37.26,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,是個男的的話
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.33,0:59:39.13,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,滿腔熱血！勇往直前！
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.28,0:59:41.17,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,滿腔熱血！勇往直前！
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.30,0:59:43.20,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,嘿喲！嘿喲！
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.25,0:59:45.19,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,嘿喲！嘿喲！
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.25,0:59:46.77,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,好樣的！
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.02,0:59:48.31,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,挺行的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.31,0:59:49.71,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,那再來一碗！
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.18,0:59:52.26,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,當個男人！
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.05,0:59:58.40,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,在搜尋我？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.15,1:00:03.28,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,這個城裡也待不下去了…
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.43,1:00:06.79,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,要不要跟我一起回農場
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.09,1:00:08.68,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,誒 可是…
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.73,1:00:09.83,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,總有辦法的
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.24,1:00:11.98,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,羊奶價格也在上漲
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.56,1:00:13.79,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,艾利爾也一起回去
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.48,1:00:15.99,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不能再給你們添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.34,1:00:17.15,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,瑪琪雅
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.68,1:00:21.24,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,要是米朵和戴奧爾有個三長兩短
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.21,1:00:23.06,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我可…
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.55,1:00:25.29,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.70,1:00:28.05,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,想讓你給我添點麻煩
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.86,1:00:31.25,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,從小時候我就一直…
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.93,1:00:34.03,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,想幫上瑪琪雅的忙
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.82,1:00:37.34,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,希望你好好考慮一下 瑪琪雅
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.88,1:00:39.88,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,將來的事情
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.63,1:00:41.26,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,還有…
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.46,1:00:44.45,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我的事情
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.95,1:01:03.12,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,恐怕不行…
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.52,1:01:04.43,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,根本不容考慮
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.45,1:01:09.82,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,一直以來我只惦記著艾利爾的事情
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.91,1:01:14.74,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,要怎麼樣才能和艾利爾一起生活下去
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.13,1:01:19.00,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,要怎麼樣才能變得像個媽媽
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.42,1:01:24.12,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,可是完全不行 根本找不到答案
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.83,1:01:29.94,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,現在 依然沒什麼找到答案的頭緒
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.50,1:01:35.14,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,因為我不怎麼聰明
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.42,1:01:39.58,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,只有艾利爾的事情 接下來…
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.66,1:01:42.11,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,想一直考慮下去
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.65,1:01:49.52,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.55,1:01:51.23,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不過
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.20,1:01:56.30,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,讓我也幫你們找找接下來的去處和工作吧
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.20,1:01:58.57,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不要什麼都自己一肩挑
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.42,1:02:31.28,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,艾利爾？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.04,1:02:37.31,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.92,1:02:40.08,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你怎麼一身酒氣
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.67,1:02:41.83,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.01,1:02:43.46,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,這可不是說「我回來了」的時候
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.72,1:02:44.79,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你到底怎麼了艾利爾
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.79,1:02:46.29,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,迎接我的吻呢
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.28,1:02:51.33,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,明明以前是絕對少不了的
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.94,1:02:55.65,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.59,1:02:58.48,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,吶 你還站得起來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.12,1:03:04.08,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,咱們 都被人家說是 私奔的了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.73,1:03:08.41,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,說你要被別的男人搶走了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.72,1:03:11.03,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.24,1:03:12.04,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.21,1:03:12.98,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,站起來
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.55,1:03:15.21,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,要睡的話到床上去…
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.26,1:03:26.22,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,還走得動嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.75,1:03:34.65,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不要踩！
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.12,1:03:42.89,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.64,1:03:46.57,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不是艾利爾織給我的嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.58,1:03:53.47,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我受不了了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.27,1:03:58.31,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,為什麼要把這種東西當寶貝啊！
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.45,1:04:01.20,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,總把我當小孩！
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.54,1:04:31.01,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,這是我永遠不變的
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.65,1:04:37.07,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,最珍貴的寶物
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.44,1:04:42.31,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,艾利爾！
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.80,1:04:49.11,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,那個 艾利爾
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.80,1:04:52.33,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我們又得搬家了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.22,1:04:55.77,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,接下來想去哪兒啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.39,1:04:58.02,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,去哪兒都行 我的話
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.56,1:05:00.99,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,只要能和艾利爾一起
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.71,1:05:03.68,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,可是我
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.57,1:05:07.44,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,從來沒把你當作母親
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.65,1:05:35.01,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,能請你幫忙說說情
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.55,1:05:37.14,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,讓我當守城衛兵嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.20,1:05:42.26,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.33,1:05:44.98,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,瑪琪雅會傷心的
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.82,1:05:47.23,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,她又不是我母親
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.86,1:05:49.86,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你說了？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.15,1:05:53.77,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你把這個跟瑪琪雅說了？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.80,1:05:55.68,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,說了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.89,1:05:59.06,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你可知道
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.52,1:06:02.34,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,瑪琪雅是怎麼一把屎一把尿把你養大的啊！
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.74,1:06:04.69,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你要撒嬌也別這麼過分！
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.49,1:06:07.14,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,從你這個年紀開始
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.30,1:06:09.65,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,瑪琪雅就拚命想當好母親
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.17,1:06:10.99,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你居然！
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.09,1:06:12.89,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,是啊 我一點都不懂！
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.01,1:06:19.65,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,為什麼那個人 要這麼地珍愛我
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.58,1:06:24.50,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,艾利爾
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.25,1:06:26.93,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,她總是在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.86,1:06:30.17,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,為了我不惜一切
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.25,1:06:34.52,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我一直以為這就是所謂母親
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.46,1:06:38.12,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,所以一直叫她媽媽
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.46,1:06:42.77,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我是那麼想保護她
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.95,1:06:49.68,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,但是如今的我是保護不了她的
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.76,1:06:52.00,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,反而
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.87,1:06:54.91,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,會傷害到她
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.23,1:06:58.55,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我終於意識到了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.81,1:07:03.26,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我是…保護不了她的！
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.39,1:07:18.30,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,看到你像這樣呱呱大哭
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.14,1:07:20.85,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,就好像看到嬰兒時候的你
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.60,1:07:27.85,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,真的要麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.77,1:07:49.85,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不用了 我自己收拾
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.27,1:07:51.80,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你不是也要走了麼
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.73,1:07:54.89,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,等把艾利爾送走以後我再走
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.09,1:08:09.20,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,注意安全 艾利爾
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.95,1:08:12.98,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,早點回來
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.65,1:08:19.54,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.21,1:08:57.12,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我不哭…的
Dialogue: 0,1:08:58.40,1:08:59.38,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我不哭
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.32,1:09:01.37,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,約好了的
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.78,1:09:07.73,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,大騙子 艾利爾
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.78,1:09:10.80,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你不是約好了要保護我的嗎…
Dialogue: 0,1:09:14.31,1:09:15.33,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,騙子…
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.76,1:09:18.80,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,討厭啊
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.42,1:10:33.52,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.89,1:10:36.60,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,本來以為能見到真的雷納托的
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.88,1:10:38.32,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,沒法子啊
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.45,1:10:43.31,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,以前曾經有好多好多 現在只剩下城裡那一頭了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:44.51,1:10:47.36,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,用這麼個虛張聲勢的雷納托遊行
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.44,1:10:49.92,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,怎麼可能提高士氣
Dialogue: 0,1:10:50.56,1:10:52.01,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,說起來你聽說了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.40,1:10:54.99,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,說是拜埃拉國搞到了妖爾夫
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.04,1:10:56.82,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,拜埃拉？ 真的假的
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.39,1:11:04.11,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,師團長長官 別再烤蝨子了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.62,1:11:05.37,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.96,1:11:06.99,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,朗格師團長長官
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.87,1:11:12.73,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,是的 確實在找
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.59,1:11:16.66,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,說是和蕾莉雅太子妃看上去差不多年紀的少女
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.23,1:11:21.02,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,並不一定是瑪琪雅
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.16,1:11:23.00,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你擔心嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.15,1:11:25.00,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,那個人
Dialogue: 0,1:11:25.63,1:11:26.78,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,是很堅強的
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.03,1:11:31.39,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,這話要是講給瑪琪雅聽 她一定會開心的
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.35,1:11:35.14,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,她總是在擔心自己能不能保護好艾利爾
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.65,1:11:38.69,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,即便如此 還是不顧一切
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.83,1:11:44.18,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,想讓你覺得她是個可以依賴的 成熟的母親
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.45,1:11:47.29,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你還真是個毛頭小子
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.65,1:11:54.18,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,或許我是個毛頭小子
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.33,1:11:55.99,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.60,1:11:59.02,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我要當個父親
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.57,1:12:08.71,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,梅薩蒂
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.17,1:12:10.58,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,那個外強中乾的國家
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.11,1:12:13.80,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,以上古之力冒充權力
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.01,1:12:16.72,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,一直將之褻瀆 這是何其愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.46,1:12:21.17,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我們一定會全力支持閣下
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.12,1:12:41.86,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,瑪琪雅
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.02,1:12:44.42,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,終於準備好了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.58,1:12:47.77,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你頭髮長長了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.70,1:12:51.05,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,妖爾夫只有生了孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.41,1:12:52.61,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,才能把頭髮留到及腰
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.30,1:12:55.19,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,來吧 瑪琪雅
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.86,1:12:57.30,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,讓我們去迎接蕾莉雅
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.50,1:13:07.89,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,要打仗了麼
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.70,1:13:10.58,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,難受的不過是一瞬
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.41,1:13:12.94,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,而且這些年來
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.26,1:13:15.35,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你熬過了比這更深沉的痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.52,1:13:20.32,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,離開妖爾夫 失去了一切
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.85,1:13:23.54,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,就好像墜入地獄一般獨守深穴
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.74,1:13:25.46,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我說啊
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.75,1:13:29.20,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你終於能理解我們的心情了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.03,1:13:31.60,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,大家四分五落
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.87,1:13:34.93,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,長老恐怕也已經不在人世了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.26,1:13:38.97,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我們一直在體味失去一切的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,1:13:39.81,1:13:40.82,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,而在這段時間
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.57,1:13:44.06,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,只有你 一直那麼幸福
Dialogue: 0,1:13:45.23,1:13:48.56,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,妖爾夫的子民 是要大家同織一塊布的
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.24,1:13:51.36,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我和蕾莉雅和瑪琪雅
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.71,1:13:54.72,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我們三個人的往昔 是不能相違的
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.13,1:14:06.65,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,恭喜了 瑪琪雅
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.30,1:14:09.95,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,就此 只屬於你的過去消失了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.62,1:14:14.10,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我們將再度 攜手共織未來
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.01,1:14:36.81,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,蒂塔！
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.44,1:14:40.05,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你回來啦 艾利爾
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.53,1:14:47.57,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,今天下班這麼早啊
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.90,1:14:49.32,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你這麼關鍵的時候
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.43,1:14:50.73,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我這邊卻忙得不可開交 真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.76,1:14:54.51,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,說是生下來還要一陣子
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.97,1:14:57.35,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不過我還是擔心你
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.21,1:14:59.53,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,馬上就來吃晚飯吧
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.13,1:15:02.80,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,啊沒事不要勉強自己 我會做的
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.57,1:15:05.85,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,稍微活動活動比較好啦
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.79,1:15:09.77,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,來 坐吧坐吧
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.89,1:15:17.33,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,差不多要生了呢 真是不可思議
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.41,1:15:22.30,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,出來打工到了梅薩蒂
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.01,1:15:25.03,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,結果能夠跟艾利爾再會
Dialogue: 0,1:15:26.56,1:15:27.41,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.29,1:15:31.27,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,吶 艾利爾
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.48,1:15:34.23,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你娶我真的好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.97,1:15:39.55,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.44,1:16:07.23,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,拜埃拉軍麼
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.82,1:16:09.28,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不只拜埃拉的船
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.06,1:16:11.92,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,還有優格 還有恩多拉！
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.56,1:16:19.89,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,艾利爾 等等
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.33,1:16:23.48,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你要保護好肚子裡的孩子
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.88,1:16:42.88,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,來太晚了 艾利爾
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.30,1:16:44.13,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.24,1:16:54.70,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,接報拜埃拉軍已經突破了山口
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.10,1:16:55.90,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我們兵分兩路…
Dialogue: 0,1:17:01.51,1:17:02.51,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,真是諷刺
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.65,1:17:15.81,Narration - chs,Narration,0,0,0,,梅薩蒂為了誇示自己的實力 利用了遠古之力
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.67,1:17:17.79,Narration - chs,Narration,0,0,0,,可這卻反而
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.28,1:17:21.61,Narration - chs,Narration,0,0,0,,讓周邊諸國齊心協力
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.94,1:17:25.03,Narration - chs,Narration,0,0,0,,懲罰濫用遠古之力的梅薩蒂
Dialogue: 0,1:17:35.41,1:17:36.91,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,大臣都去哪了！
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.53,1:17:40.85,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,據說他們跟隨從人員已經離開了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.82,1:17:43.61,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,難道他們拋棄我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:17:44.07,1:17:45.94,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,這可如何是好
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.90,1:17:49.88,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,已經完蛋了 要說再見了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.00,1:17:52.62,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,陛下 請抓緊
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.13,1:17:55.28,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,喂 梅朵梅爾小公主怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.24,1:17:57.62,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,別提這個不吉利的名字
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.74,1:18:00.96,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不需要那種東西 和她媽一起丟掉
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.69,1:18:52.96,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,瑪琪雅 我們走
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.89,1:19:29.64,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,艾利爾！
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.63,1:19:33.23,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,艾利爾！
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.44,1:19:52.21,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,蕾莉雅
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.01,1:19:55.10,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,終於找到你了
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.85,1:19:58.77,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,克里姆？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.50,1:20:01.38,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.98,1:20:04.00,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你還活著？
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.26,1:20:07.61,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我看到的…
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.33,1:20:12.35,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不是幽靈吧
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.89,1:20:18.97,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我來接你了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.80,1:20:21.57,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,將來
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.51,1:20:24.37,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,要讓那些讓你痛苦的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.14,1:20:27.17,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,受到比你更加揪心的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.08,1:20:30.93,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,然後讓一切… 都重新來過
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.00,1:20:31.70,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.24,1:20:36.17,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我想見她
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.09,1:20:39.01,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我的…女兒
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.53,1:20:41.78,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.73,1:20:45.99,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,那不是他們逼著你生下的違心的存在麼
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.32,1:20:48.63,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,但是 那是我生下的…
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.63,1:20:49.84,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,忘掉就好了！
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.39,1:20:53.58,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你的昔日織上 並沒有女兒的名字
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.84,1:20:54.99,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,可… 可是
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.58,1:21:02.90,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我以為克里姆 還有大家… 都死了…
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.80,1:21:13.06,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我以為已經失去了一切
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.88,1:21:18.28,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,所以 我心裡唯一惦記的 是我的女兒
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.75,1:21:22.24,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,只想見到她
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.94,1:21:25.95,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,只想擁抱她
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.18,1:21:31.32,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,這是我苟活至今的唯一動力
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.88,1:21:34.71,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,蕾莉雅
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.77,1:21:40.20,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我的…梅朵梅爾…
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.58,1:21:56.54,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我知道了 蕾莉雅
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.83,1:21:59.74,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,讓我們一起
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.86,1:22:01.89,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,在此走向終點吧
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.80,1:22:06.60,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,克里姆
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.40,1:22:13.21,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不會再讓…
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.80,1:22:20.04,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,別人…
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.06,1:22:24.72,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,玷汙我們的…
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.94,1:22:27.06,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,昔日織
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.29,1:22:36.10,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,克里姆
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.03,1:22:41.07,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,蕾莉雅太子妃！
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.41,1:23:14.85,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,到底是為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.01,1:23:17.06,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,為什麼蕾莉雅
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.72,1:23:18.67,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,為什麼瑪琪雅
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.40,1:23:20.36,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.86,1:23:25.27,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,為什麼她們都讓…時光流轉
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.00,1:24:05.88,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,就像那天…一樣…
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.19,1:24:33.83,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,艾利爾
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.97,1:24:36.90,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,師團長長官
Dialogue: 0,1:24:37.89,1:24:42.20,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,有情報稱拜埃拉的船上有一對妖爾夫少年少女
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.74,1:24:46.26,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你已經見到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.01,1:24:49.61,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.01,1:24:51.78,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你不用管了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.14,1:24:54.10,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,這裡交給我們 你去瑪琪雅…
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.10,1:24:55.14,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我要戰鬥下去！
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.48,1:24:58.80,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你對梅薩蒂就這麼忠誠麼
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.23,1:25:00.03,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.37,1:25:02.34,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你不過是想躲著瑪琪雅…
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.34,1:25:02.97,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不是的！
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.70,1:25:07.04,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,確實 一開始是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,1:25:08.16,1:25:10.62,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,可是如今 我有了蒂塔
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.35,1:25:12.30,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,有了兄弟
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.07,1:25:14.67,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,還有即將誕生的小寶寶
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.90,1:25:16.77,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我們梅薩蒂
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.49,1:25:18.82,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,是從那個人身邊離開以後
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.06,1:25:21.21,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,自己親手打造的第一個家
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.64,1:25:22.95,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我想要守護我的家園！
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.71,1:25:44.78,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.29,1:25:52.00,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你不是…
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.05,1:25:52.79,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我去叫醫生
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.22,1:25:53.97,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.33,1:25:57.13,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,在這種時候...
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.38,1:25:57.98,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.46,1:26:01.58,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,這是艾利爾的…
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.60,1:26:03.61,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,小寶寶
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.41,1:26:11.34,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,開炮！
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.73,1:26:32.94,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,開槍！
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.03,1:26:37.70,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,蒂塔
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.68,1:26:41.81,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,加油 馬上就能
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.59,1:26:43.98,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,見到小寶寶了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:04.92,1:27:06.27,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,沒錯沒錯 真能幹
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.66,1:27:09.69,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,蒂塔 還有一點點
Dialogue: 0,1:27:11.62,1:27:12.86,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,還有一點點了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:14.58,1:27:15.22,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,蒂塔！
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.37,1:27:23.46,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,別怕死！
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.25,1:27:33.88,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我怕…
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.91,1:27:36.44,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,蒂塔
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.44,1:27:38.21,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我好怕 好害怕！
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.40,1:27:40.11,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,救命啊…
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.11,1:27:41.58,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,蒂塔 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.98,1:27:42.37,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\an1}救救小寶寶…
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.76,1:27:45.69,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,救救我的小寶寶啊！
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.69,1:27:46.60,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我會救你們的
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.96,1:27:48.77,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你們會得救的！
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.90,1:27:54.26,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,黎明就在眼前 給我上！
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.88,1:28:10.96,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,瞧 小寶寶
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.35,1:28:12.86,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,小寶寶急著想出來呢
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.15,1:28:20.18,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,蒂塔和艾利爾就要當媽媽爸爸了！
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.83,1:28:53.84,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,堅持到最後了呢 蒂塔
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.20,1:28:56.08,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.25,1:29:16.09,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\1a&H1A&}你打算把他帶走麼
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.84,1:29:17.86,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\1a&H1A&}這可不是玩具
Dialogue: 0,1:29:17.86,1:29:19.00,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\1a&H1A&}他不是玩具
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.41,1:29:20.31,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\1a&H1A&}他是我的
Dialogue: 0,1:29:21.40,1:29:22.56,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\1a&H1A&}昔日織
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.74,1:29:26.61,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,1:29:29.03,1:29:29.97,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.31,1:29:43.96,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,艾利爾 該回家了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:44.93,1:29:46.36,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,媽媽！
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.80,1:29:48.26,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:52.09,1:29:53.88,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你都凍成這樣了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.94,1:29:58.95,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你回來啦 艾利爾
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.77,1:30:07.64,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你回來啦
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.34,1:30:11.19,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,艾利爾
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.27,1:30:15.97,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,夢…
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.93,1:30:18.29,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,這不是夢
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.39,1:30:21.84,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,可是 下雪了…
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.64,1:30:25.19,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不是雪 是灰
Dialogue: 0,1:30:36.82,1:30:39.83,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,艾利爾和蒂塔的小寶寶 生下來了
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.35,1:30:44.31,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,還不能勉強
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.00,1:30:47.87,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,沒關係的 大家都在等著艾利爾回去
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.37,1:30:50.81,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,她們會一直等著你
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.76,1:30:55.23,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,艾利爾也是像那樣
Dialogue: 0,1:30:56.24,1:30:58.27,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,從媽媽肚子裡生出來的呢
Dialogue: 0,1:31:04.56,1:31:06.05,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,艾利爾的媽媽啊
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.94,1:31:10.72,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,把艾利爾抱得那麼那麼緊
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.18,1:31:15.04,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,手指扣得是那麼緊
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.90,1:31:17.49,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,好難掰開
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.97,1:31:21.41,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,一根…又一根…
Dialogue: 0,1:31:21.95,1:31:22.77,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,別說了
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.87,1:31:23.62,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我還是…
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.15,1:31:28.34,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,沒能成為艾利爾的媽媽呢
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.34,1:31:29.33,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,別再說了！
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.80,1:31:33.43,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,是你教會了我
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.28,1:31:35.15,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,溫柔
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.88,1:31:36.76,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,堅強
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.50,1:31:38.34,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,決心
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.70,1:31:41.80,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,還有愛人之心
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.88,1:31:49.89,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,為艾利爾著想
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.89,1:31:53.51,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,就好像是為自己著想一樣
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.86,1:31:57.57,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,在跟艾利爾相遇的時候
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.32,1:32:01.88,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我想著的是 這孩子能跟我執手相看淚眼
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.30,1:32:06.19,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,想著的是 他就是我的昔日織
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.11,1:32:10.72,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,只要和艾利爾在一起
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.35,1:32:14.84,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不管是什麼樣的傷悲 什麼樣的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.02,1:32:17.32,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,都不會掀起波瀾
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.28,1:32:21.39,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,可是 我卻
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.05,1:32:22.90,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,從你身邊…
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.75,1:32:26.96,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,艾利爾從來不會騙我
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.41,1:32:31.81,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,艾利爾一直遵守著約定
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.84,1:32:36.69,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,艾利爾一直保護著我
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.16,1:32:41.21,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,哪怕雲樹遙隔 山川相阻
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.84,1:32:44.24,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,對自己都陷入迷思
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.60,1:32:48.31,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,可是只要想起艾利爾
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.75,1:32:51.04,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我就找回了自我
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.70,1:32:55.04,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,只要艾利爾還願意叫我
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.69,1:32:57.79,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,哪怕不是「媽媽」我也願意
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.76,1:33:00.08,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不管叫我什麼名字
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.82,1:33:04.52,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,這個名字一定…會成為我的名字
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.40,1:33:11.03,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,是艾利爾你 織出了今天的我
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.11,1:33:22.93,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,瑪琪雅！
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.51,1:33:28.33,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,朗格！
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.22,1:33:31.28,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,能帶艾利爾回去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:33:33.06,1:33:34.86,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,回到蒂塔和小寶寶身邊
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.39,1:33:38.71,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,回到艾利爾的歸宿
Dialogue: 0,1:33:50.42,1:33:51.39,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不要走…
Dialogue: 0,1:33:59.79,1:34:00.93,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不要走啊！
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.70,1:34:02.92,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,媽媽！
Dialogue: 0,1:35:10.14,1:35:13.05,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我們差不多該下去了吧 梅朵梅爾小公主
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.54,1:35:15.00,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,爸爸他們呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.12,1:35:21.62,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,這樣啊 沒關係
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.33,1:35:24.80,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,從這裡下去以後
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.05,1:35:28.05,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,等待我的是和迄今為止截然不同的生活
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.20,1:35:32.08,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,可是 即便如此 我也…
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.74,1:35:49.97,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你是誰？
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.24,1:35:54.50,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,蕾莉雅太子妃…
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.41,1:36:01.40,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你就是…
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.41,1:36:05.14,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我的…媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,1:36:10.37,1:36:12.31,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我是妖爾夫一族的蕾莉雅
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.11,1:36:18.51,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,是個假小子 瘋丫頭 男人婆
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.87,1:36:21.80,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.83,1:36:23.78,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,自由不羈
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.44,1:36:29.03,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,蕾莉雅 飛下來！
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.64,1:36:45.73,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我… 會飛！
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.75,1:36:49.24,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不要啊！
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.24,1:36:50.37,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,媽媽！
Dialogue: 0,1:37:08.80,1:37:09.62,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,瑪琪雅
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.25,1:37:13.04,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.45,1:37:15.98,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你也飛起來了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:37:22.74,1:37:23.80,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,再見！
Dialogue: 0,1:37:24.50,1:37:26.20,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,忘了我！
Dialogue: 0,1:37:26.77,1:37:28.16,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我也會忘掉
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.93,1:37:31.81,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,城堡裡的生活 今日的晨曦
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.93,1:37:33.40,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我是不會寫在昔日織上的！
Dialogue: 0,1:37:33.96,1:37:34.99,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.53,1:37:39.16,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,在漫漫記憶之中 把它淡忘
Dialogue: 0,1:37:40.12,1:37:41.65,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我會把這一切忘卻
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.98,1:37:43.46,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,是的…
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.58,1:37:46.42,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,這不過是一點點瑕疵！
Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.59,1:37:52.07,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,吶
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.79,1:37:53.27,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.79,1:37:57.60,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我媽媽 真是個漂亮的人
Dialogue: 0,1:38:01.94,1:38:03.07,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,梅朵梅爾小公主
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.03,1:38:06.94,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,雷納托！
Dialogue: 0,1:38:12.86,1:38:14.01,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,蕾莉雅太子妃…
Dialogue: 0,1:38:16.35,1:38:17.66,Narration - chs,Narration,0,0,0,,不需要什麼雷納托
Dialogue: 0,1:38:18.64,1:38:19.94,Narration - chs,Narration,0,0,0,,不需要什麼妖爾夫
Dialogue: 0,1:38:20.69,1:38:23.33,Narration - chs,Narration,0,0,0,,這些太古傳承的生命終將走向滅亡
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.24,1:38:24.88,Narration - chs,Narration,0,0,0,,那麼至少
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.81,1:38:28.35,Narration - chs,Narration,0,0,0,,最後能讓他們放飛自己的心靈
Dialogue: 0,1:38:34.34,1:38:36.31,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,不要哭了 蕾莉雅
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.29,1:38:44.57,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,沒關係的 你是絕對不會忘記的
Dialogue: 0,1:38:56.59,1:38:57.77,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我好難過
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.93,1:39:02.15,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,那麼難受 那麼痛苦
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.43,1:39:06.98,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,可是 世界這麼美麗…
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.94,1:39:09.70,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,讓我如何能夠忘懷
Dialogue: 0,1:39:42.80,1:39:43.65,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.31,1:39:47.57,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你回來了…
Dialogue: 0,1:39:49.34,1:39:50.50,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,這不是當然的嗎
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.12,1:39:54.91,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,這是我的…
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.39,1:40:07.39,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,她是這麼柔軟 讓人好怕…
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.62,1:40:15.76,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,得給她起個名字呢
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.15,1:40:18.84,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,蒂塔？
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.94,1:40:20.93,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.63,1:40:24.17,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我們孩提時候
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.39,1:40:29.65,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我對你說了「哪有喜歡媽媽的」
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.89,1:40:31.89,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,這種話
Dialogue: 0,1:40:33.84,1:40:35.52,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,明明一點都不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.41,1:40:38.42,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,艾利爾的媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.99,1:40:40.17,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,是那麼美麗
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.03,1:40:42.17,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,那麼溫柔
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.13,1:40:44.81,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.05,1:40:51.01,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,這孩子也是…
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.38,1:40:52.12,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我愛你
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.68,1:40:54.82,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我也是…
Dialogue: 0,1:40:55.94,1:40:56.97,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,可是我…
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.95,1:41:01.52,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,一直都嫉妒艾利爾的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,1:41:04.26,1:41:08.16,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,媽媽養大的我 愛上了你
Dialogue: 0,1:41:10.12,1:41:12.62,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,這個孩子也一定會遇上她的愛
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.70,1:41:15.41,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,把她養大吧 我們一起
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.78,1:41:19.13,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我和蒂塔 兩個人一起
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.41,1:41:23.72,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,讓她將來能夠愛上誰
Dialogue: 0,1:41:30.03,1:41:31.40,Narration - chs,Narration,0,0,0,,別離之族
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.16,1:41:35.17,Narration - chs,Narration,0,0,0,,送走人間種種別離
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.21,1:41:38.08,Narration - chs,Narration,0,0,0,,送走世間種種變遷
Dialogue: 0,1:41:39.33,1:41:42.56,Narration - chs,Narration,0,0,0,,逝者如斯 時光永遠不會止步
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.54,1:41:47.61,Narration - chs,Narration,0,0,0,,所以 我們會再度與人萍水相逢
Dialogue: 0,1:41:49.97,1:41:50.86,Narration - chs,Narration,0,0,0,,相識相知
Dialogue: 0,1:41:52.12,1:41:53.25,Narration - chs,Narration,0,0,0,,一同織下我們的人生
Dialogue: 0,1:42:08.56,1:42:09.54,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.58,1:42:16.49,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,能帶我到你爺爺那裡去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.52,1:42:18.66,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,爺爺？
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.77,1:42:19.92,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,莉莉！
Dialogue: 0,1:42:20.45,1:42:22.81,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,怎麼能這樣呢 你一直在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.16,1:42:26.09,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.06,1:42:32.59,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,媽媽三年前就去世了
Dialogue: 0,1:42:33.29,1:42:35.09,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,生前他們是一對恩愛夫妻
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.84,1:42:37.46,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,梅薩蒂失守以後
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.86,1:42:40.28,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,經朗格介紹回到了這裡
Dialogue: 0,1:42:41.72,1:42:43.25,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,雖然也有過艱辛
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.65,1:42:45.78,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,但我相信他們有著幸福的人生
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.58,1:42:54.06,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,別急別急
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.06,1:42:56.60,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,他們也經常說起你來
Dialogue: 0,1:42:57.39,1:42:59.56,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,說到你的時候 他們是那麼幸福
Dialogue: 0,1:43:00.69,1:43:02.37,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你能趕上真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,1:43:03.27,1:43:04.87,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,爸爸他 已經…
Dialogue: 0,1:43:35.63,1:43:36.47,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,1:43:37.16,1:43:37.97,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,艾利爾
Dialogue: 0,1:43:48.65,1:43:50.90,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,真了不起 艾利爾
Dialogue: 0,1:43:55.40,1:43:56.28,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你是這麼…
Dialogue: 0,1:44:00.29,1:44:04.03,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,這麼努力地 活下來的呢…
Dialogue: 0,1:44:04.46,1:44:05.29,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,艾利爾
Dialogue: 0,1:44:11.13,1:44:12.19,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我不哭的
Dialogue: 0,1:44:13.14,1:44:15.44,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我跟你…約好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:44:29.75,1:44:33.67,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,你回…來了啊…
Dialogue: 0,1:44:42.38,1:44:43.35,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,1:45:32.17,1:45:34.42,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,注意安全啊 艾利爾
Dialogue: 0,1:45:36.26,1:45:37.70,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,吃晚飯的時候
Dialogue: 0,1:45:38.50,1:45:39.92,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,要回來啊
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.31,1:45:47.22,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,送給你
Dialogue: 0,1:45:48.13,1:45:49.16,Sayo Asa - chs,,0,0,0,,謝謝
